sep.gaia.util

Class FloatVector3D

  • java.lang.Object
    • sep.gaia.util.FloatVector3D
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Vector3D

    public class FloatVector3D
extends java.lang.Object
implements Vector3D
    Class to represent a 3-dimensional vector with float coordinates. Instances of this class may also be used as 2-dimensional vectors by following the convention of setting the z-coordinate 0.
    Author:
    Max Witzelsperger
